Educational thinking: How to make “Xueba” and “Xueba” have their own place in university exams-Xinhua
Three students from Lanzhou Jiaotong University wrote to the school leaders to reflect their confusion about the university examination, and proposed to increase the difficulty of the examination and change the question types of the examination so that the examination truly reflects the actual level of the students' demands.
Indeed, for a long time, university exams have been a “hot topic”.
On university campuses, students come from all over the world, with different levels of ability, coupled with different levels of learning, the learning situation is very different.
For the assessment of groups with such diverse characteristics, it is inevitable that there are different feelings.
Of course, if the exam question type is single, the repetition rate is high, and the question is too simple, it will inevitably cause another very different feeling.
Students who don't need to work hard may be able to pass the exam by concentrating on assault before the exam. If you think of other methods, it is possible to achieve a multiplier effect with half the effort.
In this way, there has been a “strange status quo” that “Xueba” can pass the exam without investment, and even get a high score; “Xueba” usually never leaves class, homework and notes are good, and the exam is not much higher.
From this point of view, the students of Lanzhou Jiaotong University reflect that the problems in the university examination are not for no reason, and I believe that this situation does not only exist in Lanzhou Jiaotong University.
In this sense, I would like to praise these three students who wrote straightforwardly.
In fact, people who have been to university know that it is not uncommon to prepare for the exam unannounced, think of various ways to “get” the exam questions from the teacher, strive to narrow the scope of the exam, and obtain “key guidance” before the exam. It is not uncommon to even entrain a cheat sheet in the exam and ask the teacher to raise his hand after the exam. It is not an anecdote.
In the author's view, as a kind of teaching quality evaluation guide, measuring the passability of a university examination lies more in the teacher's comprehensive grasp of teaching and learning, as well as the scientific proposition on this basis.
Entering the undergraduate stage of the university, the majors begin to be subdivided, and many professional courses focus on basic knowledge.
There is no doubt that whether to fully grasp the basic knowledge points of a subject is the content to be examined in the university examination.
The undergraduate knowledge is basically the basic theory and basic common sense of the subject. From the point of view of knowledge, the room for change is not large, and it is basically fixed.
As a teacher said, “I studied the basic knowledge of mathematics in college 20 years ago, but I am still studying it now, and it is still the focus.  ”
However, the knowledge points are basically the same, which does not mean that the test question type is single or the test questions are repeated.
In many universities, exams generally form a question group, and then senior teachers in the subject co-ordinate the composition of the test papers. The examination papers are also participated by all the teachers who undertake the subject, so that the repetition of the test questions can be overcome to a certain extent. The situation.
However, it is necessary to draw up a set of test questions that are in line with the actual situation of teaching and learning. The questions are normally distributed according to the overall situation of students' learning. It is also necessary to comprehensively grasp the teaching situation and comprehensively analyze the degree of students' learning, so that the test propositions have a dynamic grasp of the difficulty and question types, which can not only highlight the basic knowledge examination, but also take into account the ability examination, and at the same time carry out innovative design of the question types.
Exams are the baton of university education. What kind of exams are there, students will have corresponding exam preparation plans. In the long run, it will affect the effectiveness of university education.
Lanzhou Jiaotong University attaches great importance to the students' letter of suggestion, and has deployed a rectification plan throughout the school.
All teaching units are required to organize teachers to conduct seminars and self-examination of course completion exams, formulate exam paper propositions and related systems, and strengthen the supervision and inspection of exam paper propositions and review links, refine the performance evaluation, and strengthen the comprehensive assessment of all aspects of curriculum teaching.
Mechanically solving the problems of single types of test questions and repeated questions is an issue that universities need to face in the examination affairs. Of course, corresponding systems need to be introduced, but effort is expensive in daily life and teachers need to have a comprehensive grasp of the teaching situation. It is necessary not only to understand the teaching content, but also to understand the student's learning situation. Both ends will be thoroughly fed. Teaching and learning will be better connected, forming a healthy interaction, and the examination will be more in line with reality, so that “Xueba” and “Xueba” have their own place.
