The notice requires that efforts be made from nine aspects, including improving the epidemic prevention and control mechanism of port cities, improving the epidemic monitoring and early warning system, and implementing border control measures, to accelerate the completion of the shortcomings of port cities' prevention and control, and to do a good job in prevention and control without relaxation, scientifically and accurately, and to weave a tight line of defense against foreign imports.
